org.drip.product.params

Class PeriodSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.service.stream.Serializer
      • org.drip.product.params.PeriodSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PeriodGenerator

    public class PeriodSet
extends Serializer
implements Validatable
    This is the place-holder for the component’s period generation parameters. Contains the component's date adjustment parameters for period start/end, period accrual start/end, effective, maturity, pay and reset, first coupon date, and interest accrual start date.
